  ('social-worker-moex-06918', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-102-a62ebd66', 'sub-social-worker-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '在一所卓越大學「學生學習態度」的研究中，以學院、學系、班級做為依序層級，再依固定比例隨機抽 樣，分別抽取研究對象，請問這個方法是下列那一項？', '["簡單隨機抽樣（simple random sampling）", "系統抽樣（systematic sampling）", "分層比例抽樣（proportionate stratified sampling）", "分層非比例抽樣（disproportionate stratified sampling）"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:36+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "1d0f7c4c7766", "answer_pdf_sha1": "06556a0af8b4", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "102030", "c": "111", "s": "0706", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作研究方法", "year": "102", "exam_name": "102年第一次專技醫師中醫師分試中醫師營養師心理師醫事檢驗師護理師社會工作師、特考聽力牙體語言治療師考試", "original_question_number": 36, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-06919', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-102-a62ebd66', 'sub-social-worker-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '冬天裡，小盧經常看到街友瑟縮在騎樓的角落，因此他常去街友出現的街道訪問，請問他用那一種抽樣 方法？', '["便利抽樣（convenience sampling）", "配額抽樣（quota sampling）", "滾雪球抽樣（snowball sampling）", "叢集抽樣（cluster sampling）"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:36+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "1d0f7c4c7766", "answer_pdf_sha1": "06556a0af8b4", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "102030", "c": "111", "s": "0706", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作研究方法", "year": "102", "exam_name": "102年第一次專技醫師中醫師分試中醫師營養師心理師醫事檢驗師護理師社會工作師、特考聽力牙體語言治療師考試", "original_question_number": 37, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL)
